text: Mi pen thi na tahni kæ phwk nang keiyw kab bida khxng phwk nang læa luk «khxng phwk nang læa phinxng phuchay khxng phwk nang læa lukchay khxng phinxng hying khxng phwk nang læa brrda phuhying khxng phwk nang læa sing thi muxkhwa khxng phwk nang khrxbkhrxng læa phwk nang ya ke rng tx xallxhˌ thæcring xallxhˌ nan thrng pen phyan tx thuk sing
